item.title: Network Visualization in R
item.description: It’s been some time since the last post! Classes picked up and we’re in the prime selling season at office, so I let the blog simmer. The below is the write up for one of my courses this past semester - Information Visualization. Images come from the awesome article by Hafsa Jabeen on basket analysis. You can find the associated shiny app here. Setting this up is deserving of its own write up, so I’ll get to it another time.
